social_posts.post_text: Outtakes // Someone came over to my old apt. once and mentioned the ‘famous mirror’ 🪞✨
I miss shooting part one ✨ 📸: @eriktranberg x @arsenic x anouk
2022 you’ve been good to me; some of my fav random moments with some of my fav people - I apologize in advance that IG is rude and limits how many clips i can add 🫶🏼😭💫🥹 #nye

Happy 2023 babies‼️‼️ I know i’ve gone mostly hermit-mode in terms of social media for the past few months (last 2 especially) BUTTTT that is b/c I’ve thrown myself 150% into adapting my first Screenplay into a Limited Series + started my 2nd(‼️‼️🥹) business right before the New year (like literally the week of NYE - Workaholics unite 🤘🏼✨) so ill have some V exciting things to share with you bb’s in the upcoming months! In other news - I’m also OFFICIALLY on the @playboy site as one of their first ever bunnies on their new exclusive content platform - Hit my @hoo.be l!nk above ⬆️ for all the newest updates you don’t want to miss my loves ‼️🫶🏼✨ #playboybunnies

Finally got around to shooting some fresh content in the new house 🏡‼️✨ And just in time for my latest delivery of my FAV microdosing supplement 🍄✨🫶🏼 It’s no secret I’m high-strung as hell, and my career choice isn’t exactly ‘relaxing’ - Here’s one of my secrets to staying (somewhat) sane ✨✨✨ Hit the l!ñk !n b!¡0 for the full spread hehe ✨

Another year around the sun 🌞 (a tad late on this post considering my actual birthday was on the 8th but life, ya know?) ‼️😅✨ This year has been a whirlwind, some good, some bad, some downright life changing; but all-around i’m endlessly grateful for this little thing called life, and the people that make even the tiniest moments incredible ✨ Here’s to 26 and to accomplishing more this year (i have quite a few projects in the works I can’t wait to share with you bb’s when i’m able) than ever before ✨🫶🏼‼️🫶🏼✨ 

xox
When the inspiration strikes ⚡️ @stefachka we may not have managed to film our feature yet so here’s a lil taste - the world is NOTTTTT ready 🌎🤘🏼😂✨

BTS at its finest from our very first shoot at the new house 🏡‼️ IG vs. Reality in fast forward ⏩  The shots from the @midsommarmovie inspired scene is EVERYTHING ‼️‼️‼️ Full stop coming soon bb’s ;) ✨
Created some magic at home the other day ✨Straight from the camera b/c who needs filters when you have good natural light? 📸 ✨🫶🏼✨ the OGs know where to find the rest hehe ‼️

It’s Friday bb’s ‼️ Happy to officially announce, that I’ve joined the @playboycenterfold bunny family and that’s where I’ll be sharing more of a look into my daily life 🐰✨ 📣 Can’t wait to continue growing and getting to know you lil bunnies ‼️✨🫶🏼

2023 so far in 30 seconds ✨ Sometime’s it’s too easy to get stressed out about little things, or situations entirely out of our control - So here’s my gentle reminder to myself, and to all of you bb’s, to take a moment, and be proud of everything you’ve accomplished so far ‼️🥹 And be kinder to yourself 🫶🏼 One of my favorite things about acting is the fact that everything IS captured on film, the in-between, awkward, and sometimes royally hilarious smaller moments of life are what make the entire experience that much sweeter - And it’s always a great reminder to be able to look back on 🎞️ Be your OWN main character 👑✨👑
